            "content": {
                "raw": "How about I remove `disable_warnings_logging`?  I don't think that is actually functional here.  `disable_exception_logging` is the thing that's preventing astropy from capturing yt-raised or user-raised exceptions.\n\nI'd argue that allowing astropy to capture all exceptions is not what we want either.",
                "html": "<p>How about I remove <code>disable_warnings_logging</code>?  I don't think that is actually functional here.  <code>disable_exception_logging</code> is the thing that's preventing astropy from capturing yt-raised or user-raised exceptions.</p>\n<p>I'd argue that allowing astropy to capture all exceptions is not what we want either.</p>",
                "markup": "markdown"
